{"履修期": "秋学期", "主な教授言語": "日本語", "授業目的": "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span ｍｓ=\"ｍｓ\" 明朝\";mso-ascii-font-family:times;mso-fareast-font-family:\"ｍｓ=\"明朝';mso-ascii-font-family:times;mso-fareast-font-family:'ｍｓ\" 明朝\";mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:times;mso-ansi-language:en-us;\"=\"明朝';mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:times;mso-ansi-language:en-us;'\" style=\"font-family:;\">　この授業では、フランス語の時制の特殊な用法を多角的に分析することによって、言語分析に用いられる概念と種々の言語理論の理解を深めることを目的とする。</span></p>", "到達目標": "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span ｍｓ=\"ｍｓ\" 明朝\";mso-ascii-font-family:times;mso-fareast-font-family:\"ｍｓ=\"明朝';mso-ascii-font-family:times;mso-fareast-font-family:'ｍｓ\" 明朝\";mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:times;mso-ansi-language:en-us;\"=\"明朝';mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:times;mso-ansi-language:en-us;'\" style=\"font-family:;\">本授業では、言語の仕組みと働きについて疑問を研究課題へと高めてゆく考察と分析の方法を身に付けることを目標とする。</span></p>", "特記事項": "", "関連科目": "", "授業の概要・背景": "", "授業方法": "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span ｍｓ=\"ｍｓ\" 明朝\";mso-ascii-font-family:times;mso-fareast-font-family:\"ｍｓ=\"明朝';mso-ascii-font-family:times;mso-fareast-font-family:'ｍｓ\" 明朝\";mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:times;mso-ansi-language:en-us;\"=\"明朝';mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:times;mso-ansi-language:en-us;'\" style=\"font-family:;\">　教室でレジュメを用いた講義形式で、必要に応じて討論を行う。</span></p>", "トピック": {"授業計画1": "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span ｍｓ=\"ｍｓ\" 明朝\";mso-ascii-font-family:times;mso-fareast-font-family:\"ｍｓ=\"明朝';mso-ascii-font-family:times;mso-fareast-font-family:'ｍｓ\" 明朝\";mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:times;mso-ansi-language:en-us;\"=\"明朝';mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:times;mso-ansi-language:en-us;'\" style=\"font-family:;\">　フランス語の時制の用法